title: DAZ3D - Zoe Hair for Gn3F
description:
--- Previously uploaded to KAT by dmitsh ---

Long and natural this cascading hair features tiny braids and wild flyaway strands. Zoe Hair features a natural bohemian feel that is perfect for musical festivals to historical settings.

Zoe Hair includes 16 Natural Color settings, with individual maps created for each, in both Iray and 3Delight options and 30 Morphs for just the right movement or look.
